name: Raining Ash #16
description:
Within the expanding cosmos of Copy Planet. This series of works explores the idea of evolution, gravity and collaboration. 

It is a contemplation of the sacred and the profane through the attitude and integrity of a poetical terrorist. 

Made up of 16 puzzle pieces, 4 rows of 4, 1/1 unique on https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/ in a Copy Planet’s trademark style. 

These motion works let us dive into a poetical puzzle represented as a universe of symbols and signs made up of Egyptian iconography deemed to be sacred by the artist. 

Cooked by collaborating with https://typedistortdecay.xyz/ 

By James Ly
